    <item>
      <title>埃及塞西巡游加沙连任，聚焦经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/egypt-s-sisi-cruises-to-re-election-with-gaza-economy-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总统阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西以压倒性优势第三次连任，将他对这个陷入数十年来最严重经济困境并面临再次货币贬值可能性的北非国家的统治延长至 2030 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/egypt-s-sisi-cruises-to-re-election-with-gaza-economy-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家在实现气候和清洁能源目标方面偏离轨道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/eu-states-off-track-for-hitting-climate-and-clean-energy-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟各国政府必须加紧努力，通过加速淘汰化石燃料和提高该地区清洁能源行业的竞争力，实现欧盟在十年内减排至少 55% 的约束性目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/eu-states-off-track-for-hitting-climate-and-clean-energy-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维尔德斯获胜后荷兰央行警告不要“退欧”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/dutch-central-bank-warns-against-nexit-after-wilders-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰央行一名高级官员警告称，在极右翼政治家基尔特·威尔德斯(Geert Wilders)令人震惊的选举胜利后，荷兰退出欧盟将是一个“坏主意”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/dutch-central-bank-warns-against-nexit-after-wilders-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国与立陶宛制定路线图以加强北约侧翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/germany-draws-up-roadmap-with-lithuania-to-reinforce-nato-flank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和立陶宛签署了一项计划，将在未来四年内在这个波罗的海国家驻扎一个由约 4,800 名德国士兵组成的常备旅，以加强北约在联盟东翼的防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/germany-draws-up-roadmap-with-lithuania-to-reinforce-nato-flank</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>文件揭示了俄罗斯核电站的隐藏问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/documents-reveal-hidden-problems-at-russia-s-nuclear-powerhouse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年2月，普京入侵乌克兰之初，俄罗斯军队大量涌入乌克兰，邻国白俄罗斯的克里姆林宫旗舰核项目引起了人们的警惕，该项目距离欧盟边境不远。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/documents-reveal-hidden-problems-at-russia-s-nuclear-powerhouse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:55:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将从 2027 年开始对钢铁进口征收气候税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继欧盟采取类似举措后，英国将于 2027 年对从气候规则较弱的国家进口的排放密集型商品征收碳边境税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗加油站可能遭到黑客攻击，局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/iran-fuel-stations-disrupted-by-possible-sabotage-tv-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗石油部长贾瓦德·欧吉表示，网络攻击扰乱了伊朗伊斯兰共和国多个省份加油站的燃料供应，并指责以色列、美国和加沙正在进行的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/iran-fuel-stations-disrupted-by-possible-sabotage-tv-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
